      "message": "how about making cfgclient.Get() accepting ${appid} as a placeholder? Then one can use exactly the same var.\nalso, can \"services/${appid}\" and \"${appid}.cfg\" be constants in rules package? Seems like these two would be sufficient for most packages.",
